    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《飞机失事模拟器》中你将扮演一名飞机事故调查员，亲临事故现场，收集关键证据，重建飞机残骸，找到目击证人，挖掘事故背后的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/fa9ce02776d4356a49f5fa5f4eb2bbf1.poster.avif?t=1746518880\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/fa9ce02776d4356a49f5fa5f4eb2bbf1.webm?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/fa9ce02776d4356a49f5fa5f4eb2bbf1.mp4?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亲临事故现场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以飞机事故调查员的身份，进入飞机事故现场，寻找丢失在各处的飞机残骸，利用专业的工具和设备，收集证据，保护事故现场，为后续调查提供保障。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/25f4f4e858d555a8147983b89fadd215.poster.avif?t=1746518880\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/25f4f4e858d555a8147983b89fadd215.webm?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/25f4f4e858d555a8147983b89fadd215.mp4?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重建飞机残骸</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在机库中重新组装飞机零件，还原飞机的本来面貌。不要放过蛛丝马迹，它们可能就是导致事故的罪魁祸首。将证物寄给不同的专业机构，通过分析研究排除导致飞机事故的种种原因，最终直指真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/8cbbd3b99340ea25dcfdfc28c844c728.poster.avif?t=1746518880\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/8cbbd3b99340ea25dcfdfc28c844c728.webm?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/8cbbd3b99340ea25dcfdfc28c844c728.mp4?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到目击证人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >询问目击证人，获取更多线索，还原事故发生的前因后果。究竟是人为因素，还是不幸的意外？背后的诸多秘密等待你的揭晓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/0935437628e60e2a60c24f65a25551e4.poster.avif?t=1746518880\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/0935437628e60e2a60c24f65a25551e4.webm?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/0935437628e60e2a60c24f65a25551e4.mp4?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟真实的飞机失事现场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解如何科学地处理飞机失事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲手重建坠毁的飞机</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过专业的分析研究和证人沟通找到飞机失事的原因</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/6dd999f19c6926c142325f0c32ecfdf5.poster.avif?t=1746518880\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/6dd999f19c6926c142325f0c32ecfdf5.webm?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682340/extras/6dd999f19c6926c142325f0c32ecfdf5.mp4?t=1746518880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
